</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/GTsPpRmy8aI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/11/apple-iphone-se-3-will-get-5g-connectivity-but-use-same-design-as-se/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-iphone-se-3-will-get-5g-connectivity-but-use-same-design-as-se</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Intel 廣告諷刺 Mac 不能升級【有片睇】網民大量負評</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/SIVrW-hC6l0/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 11 Oct 2021 11:44:20 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[intel]]></category><category><![CDATA[M1]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1065085</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>自 Appl M1 晶片面世後，Intel 對其的「攻擊」就沒有中斷過。除了先前的 Twitter 廣告、5  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">自 Appl M1 晶片面世後，Intel 對其的「攻擊」就沒有中斷過。除了先前的 Twitter 廣告、5 部 Intel 和 Mac 進行比較的廣告影片外，今次更找來數位自稱「忠實果粉」的 Apple 粉絲進行訪問，打算用 Apple 沒有的功能和設計來說服他們，影片一出卻引來大量負評。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/986401E2-2548-4F87-8B51-01F55B1E8F2F-694x343.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/986401E2-2548-4F87-8B51-01F55B1E8F2F-694x343.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/986401E2-2548-4F87-8B51-01F55B1E8F2F-1280x633.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/986401E2-2548-4F87-8B51-01F55B1E8F2F-768x380.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/986401E2-2548-4F87-8B51-01F55B1E8F2F-1536x760.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/986401E2-2548-4F87-8B51-01F55B1E8F2F-2048x1014.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/986401E2-2548-4F87-8B51-01F55B1E8F2F.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">在影片開始，多名受邀民眾均表示自己是徹底的 Apple 粉絲，更甚至有人說「我是 100% 忠實 Apple」、「我是 Apple 女孩、Apple 世界」。開始訪問後，第一道題目是：「你希望能自己客製化你的電腦嗎？」，每一位受訪者均表示希望可以，例如可以自己額外加 RAM；接著又開始播放 Intel 筆記型電腦可自行升級的影片，間接嘲諷 Apple 無法自行升級，在影片播放完畢後就有 Apple 粉絲表示這對他來說十分興奮。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065091" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/68EBA2B5-34E4-43ED-99C4-49B80E49619F-694x361.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="361" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/68EBA2B5-34E4-43ED-99C4-49B80E49619F-694x361.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/68EBA2B5-34E4-43ED-99C4-49B80E49619F-1280x667.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/68EBA2B5-34E4-43ED-99C4-49B80E49619F-768x400.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/68EBA2B5-34E4-43ED-99C4-49B80E49619F-1536x800.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/68EBA2B5-34E4-43ED-99C4-49B80E49619F-2048x1067.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/68EBA2B5-34E4-43ED-99C4-49B80E49619F.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">其後，屏幕亮起各種不同遊戲，數量由 1 開始遞增到 5700+，表示這些遊戲都可在一個裝置中下載使用，不少受訪者均表示興致勃勃，十分期待；來到第三個展示的設計，雙螢幕設計的，設計圖出現，問受訪民眾會否希望體驗雙可觸屏幕的電腦，有幾位說「哇」、「夠了哦！」、「我知道使用後一定會愛上」。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065088" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/F7C861A0-AE61-4C2C-9032-33EB4218D5FF-694x311.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="311" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/F7C861A0-AE61-4C2C-9032-33EB4218D5FF-694x311.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/F7C861A0-AE61-4C2C-9032-33EB4218D5FF-1280x574.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/F7C861A0-AE61-4C2C-9032-33EB4218D5FF-768x345.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/F7C861A0-AE61-4C2C-9032-33EB4218D5FF-1536x689.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/F7C861A0-AE61-4C2C-9032-33EB4218D5FF-2048x919.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/F7C861A0-AE61-4C2C-9032-33EB4218D5FF.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1065089" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/123F75E9-6500-4A19-9B61-5ABDEA843D3B-694x326.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="326" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/123F75E9-6500-4A19-9B61-5ABDEA843D3B-694x326.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/123F75E9-6500-4A19-9B61-5ABDEA843D3B-1280x601.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/123F75E9-6500-4A19-9B61-5ABDEA843D3B-768x361.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/123F75E9-6500-4A19-9B61-5ABDEA843D3B-1536x721.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/123F75E9-6500-4A19-9B61-5ABDEA843D3B.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.07.46.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1065105" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.07.46-694x359.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="359" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.07.46-694x359.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.07.46-1280x662.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.07.46-768x397.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.07.46.jpg 1297w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.08.23.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1065106" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.08.23-694x376.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.08.23-694x376.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.08.23-768x416.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/螢幕截圖-2021-10-11-19.08.23.jpg 1164w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">最後一個為二合一設計的電腦，即包括筆記型電腦和平板電腦，有不少蘋果粉絲竟表示從來沒有聽過這種設計。結束前又告訴受訪者，以上所提及的功能和設計均是 Intel 處理器的筆記型電腦，而並非他們喜歡的 Apple。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">這次的廣告影片一出引來極大量負評，在 YouTube 中 Dislike 數接近 Like 數的兩倍。更有網民留言指：「 Intel 就像分手後的前女友，想盡一切辦法看你不順眼。」</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_12314"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Xp0xzapm-zY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://youtu.be/Xp0xzapm-zY">YouTube</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
